{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3dacd732af","title":"对上海党政群机关团体编制情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7bcb3cb746","index":0,"year":1950,"month":8,"day":20,"articleId":"3dacd732af"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"373c3196a1","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dacd732af","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周，指周恩来。"},{"id":"5b3ca1456c","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dacd732af","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共上海市委1950年8月14日关于上海党政群机关团体编制情况给中央并华东局的报告中提出的两项建议。这两项建议是：（一）编余员工处理问题。整编中采取谨慎处理是非常重要的，但老弱残疾人员，应视具体情况分别处理，一般可早日给资造散。工务局六七十岁有多年工龄的老工人，无家可归者以包下养老为宜。（二）编制委员会撤销后，凡有关编制问题，应指定专门机关继续负责指导，以巩固已得成绩，并坚持贯彻下去。否则时间一久，便又各自为政，自行扩充广泛招聘、制度松解的倾向难免发生，这是值得注意的。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b92762f06a","type":"title","text":"对上海觉政群机关团体编制情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dacd732af"},{"id":"373c3196a1","type":"paragraph","text":"周“：此电两项建议值得注意，请考虑指示各地，省及大市照此办理，成为制度。又，各地整编总结，报来者少，请考虑去电催送总结。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dacd732af"},{"id":"5b3ca1456c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dacd732af"},{"id":"6b11ab80fe","type":"paragraph","text":"八月廿日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dacd732af"}],"page":{"id":"d37d020d5d","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dacd732af","start":91,"end":91}}}},"__N_SSG":true}